# Vampire - Dialogue File

@encounter
Vampire: The night is young, hunter...
Vampire: You reek of dead man's blood. Cute.

@taunt
Vampire: You think your little tricks will stop me?
Vampire: I've been around for centuries, Winchester.
Dean: Yeah, well, I've killed older.

@defeat
Vampire: No... this can't be...
Dean: Believe it, fangs.
Sam: That's another one down.
